{"tid":2321917,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(我屌你老母支共) 南韓導演金基德感染新型肺炎在拉脫維亞病逝","createTime":"2020-12-12T02:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T03:44:43.000Z","uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"32d4752d25e11384ac1a0548ff45bf82e7e1b892","tid":2321917,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:00:03.000Z","msg":"南韓電影導演金基德感染新型肺炎，在拉脫維亞首都里加一家醫院離世。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社報道，金基德上月20日抵達拉脫維亞，但本月5日起一直無法取得聯絡，他的朋友開始在當地醫院打探消息。金基德原本計劃在拉脫維亞北部置業，取得永久居留權。<br />\n<br />\n11日，一名俄羅斯的知情人士講到，60歲的導演金基德在拉脫維亞因感染新冠肺炎病逝，拉脫維亞政府第一時間查詢相關事件是否真確，確認後再通知韓國外交部。據知，金基德在上個月20日去到拉脫維亞，他在拉脫維亞的電影製片人幫助下入住當地的住所，最近因感染新冠肺炎而住院，但就在入院2天日死亡。<br />\n<br />\n而韓國外交部代表接受傳媒查詢時說：「當地時間11日凌晨，一名韓國國民（金基德）在接受新冠肺炎治療時死亡」、「駐拉脫維亞大使館在接到韓國國民死亡的消息後，通過當地醫院確認了相關經過」、「正與其遺屬接觸，亦正聯絡當地部門處理相關事項，對葬禮作出支援」。<br />\n<br />\n根據韓媒sports chosun報導，Vitaly Mansky導演跟金基德失去聯絡後，去到當地醫院找尋，才發現金基德因病離逝。出生貧窮家庭的金基德，只有初中學歷。15歲起就在工廠工作，曾經夢想成為聖職人員，但沒有完成相關學業，因此作為電影導演拍了《慾海慈航》和《阿門》、《聖殤》藉此圓夢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb3b2bde9f8816941853f52544304129a350cd0","tid":2321917,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:00:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564901-20201212.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564901-20201212.htm&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmhksnaRIvLJvZlYWuj0OsWg%3D&h=acaf6f89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564901-20201212.htm&h=6ddd0273\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564901-20201212.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0723cc24b02d4b84d4cfc3ee954631b9796497df","tid":2321917,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95f45d3e4ae894e854dce5c4597222e87f542bf","tid":2321917,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c104d00791920647475d56b11fbeee8b73c54e","tid":2321917,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e9eb57713372bec3ad04d61b5d819429a60000","tid":2321917,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b502958c94f8194a03af6c5a2dfa92cba929da","tid":2321917,"uid":85965,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:36:02.000Z","msg":"Rip,睇過聖殤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n南韓冇左個好導演"},{"pid":"fa50f73b9288d78d480015a191f328524fdc60a1","tid":2321917,"uid":34899,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> r.i.p<br />\n又一知名人士"}]}